metadata.name: DNA #1
metadata.description: Seeking a unique NFT and digital collectible experience? Look no further, intrepid explorer... you've discovered Definitely Not Aliens! Brace yourself for a warp-speed journey into a mind-bending universe, where your DNA token grants access to an epic story featuring relatable characters and awe-inspiring worlds. But exploration is just the beginning. Join us on our quest to blur the lines between reality and fantasy as we strive to take the fiction out of science fiction. Whether you’re new to NFTs or are an OG with historical pieces, there’s a place for you in this project. Embrace the thrill, venture into the unknown, and experience this journey with us! So, what are you waiting for? Collect your aliens now!
